dc_description_s: This ESRI Geodatabase contains polygon features and attribute data tables for census data for the Dominican Republic . The data is derived from the Oficina Nactional de Estadistica (ONE) and was released in 2010. The data contain 10,807 census boundary polygons that each have 249 attributes, and the lowest administrative boundary level represented is Barrios. Refer to the documentation for a list of variables and a translation of variable titles into English. For more information on the census methodology and a glossary of variable categories, go to the ONE website at http://www.one.gob.do/.
